As a sign of respect for the military members killed in his war with Iran, Trump wore the same baseball cap he wore as their caskets passed by him at Dover Air Force Base yesterday as he lumbered by the hotdog stand at his golf resort in Florida today (cap available for just $55… pic.twitter.com/FrkJL4fKwl
